             FACE IDENTIFICATION & MOTION DETECTION PROGRESS TREE
                         Version 1.0, openCV

# IMAGE
  * if a image is 500 x 700 size and a coloured image means
            it has 500 rows & 700 columns and 3 channels (R,B,G)
  * If a image is 200 x 500 and grayscale or black&white image means
            it has 200 rows & 500 columns and 1 channel

  * SIZE OF IMAGE = NO OF ROWS x NO OF COLUMNS x NO OF CHANNELS

# BASIC WORKFLOW:
# ===============
  * Image tweaks
  * Identify faces from images using cascades
  * Capture video from webcam
  * Motion detection
  * Motion detection with tracking in & out time of object
